  "body": [
    "Bhai Balvir Singh Ji is undoubtedly one of the contemporary Raagis to look out for. He is blessed with a uniquely deep and versatile voice, which he uses with great skill that leaves the Sangat wanting more. He is also adept in singing in various Raags, of which some can be heard in the recordings below. He has performed in various Raag Darbars including the annual Samagam held in Jawaddi Kalan and he has visited Malaysia many times as well. Most of the recordings below are from his tours to Malaysia. If anyone has more information or recordings of Bhai Balvir Singh Ji, please contact us.",
    "Update: We are deeply saddened to inform that Bhai Balvir Singh Ji passed away on 28th December 2022."
  ],
